Reverts https://github.com/qtproject/pyside-pyside-setup/commit/249678e5d19d5e9ef7f24d68a154da806aed4a81 ,
which fixes the build error
ImportError: dlopen failed: cannot locate symbol "PepEval_GetFrameGlobals"
referenced by "/data/data/com.termux/files/home/.termux-build/pyside6/build/sources/pyside6/PySide6/QtCore.cpython-312.so"...
while building using Python 3.12 (it is assumed that building with Python 3.13 would have a different result)

diff --git a/sources/pyside6/libpyside/feature_select.cpp b/sources/pyside6/libpyside/feature_select.cpp
